features
    Icecream
        mandatory
            Container
                alternative
                    Cup
                    Cone 
                    Stick 
        optional
            Integer Scoops
constraints
    Cone => Scoops == 1
    Cup => Scoops >= 1 & Scoops <= 3
    Stick => !Scoops
    Scoops >= 1 & Scoops <= 3